column5: Due to some personal family issues I will have to attend to on Saturday, looks like ill not be making the trip the the Tyler Event this year.  So I've shipped off a bunch of stuff to Elisa for the prize table.  But hey why stop there... so from now till tomorrow noon I'm gonna reduce my flat shipping rate to 5 bucks and donate 10 percent of my gross sales to Fishing for Tyler.  If you haven't donated yet, and/or are not going to the event, this is a great way to get some good tackle and support a worthy cause (and yes.. lol. help me move some inventory.)  Have a look around, ill be adding stuff all day.  http://www.duenorthfishinglures.com
Nice move T.J... Hope all is okay though...
No worries, everything is ok.. just gotta do something with my dad.
Always doing for others, good on ya TJ
That okay then.. do what you have to do.. Don't need any more bad news..  getting tired of hearing of it ..Take care
Very generous as always TJ  Maureen
Got some orders out today... Thanks all!!    I think ill run the offer till Monday!!
